# Egress allowlist FQDNs for the active observability provider.
# One FQDN per line. Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
# These are resolved into ipset 'obs_egress_ips' at install time and refreshed
# daily by newrelic-egress-refresh.timer.
#
# New Relic EU region (GDPR-required for UK/EU hosts).
# https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/new-relic-solutions/get-started/networks/
infra-api.eu.newrelic.com
metric-api.eu.newrelic.com
log-api.eu.newrelic.com
identity-api.eu.newrelic.com
